title: Bill Gates SLAMMED By Joe Rogan, Russel Brand For Driving Vaccine Conversations, Motivated By Profit
cleaned_text: Batya Ungar-Sargon and Robby Soave talk about the conversation between podcaster Joe Rogan and comedian Russell Brand criticizing Bill Gates inserting himself in public health matters. Originally aired March 6, 2023.
